Color notes and photos of live breeding adults (
PSU 12758
). Males in territorial color with light blue ground coloration and 5–6 distinct black bars. Head black with 2 light blue interorbital bars; throat dark brown. Anal fin black with 4–6 yellow ocelli; light yellow marginal band. Pectoral-fin rays black with clear membranes ( Fig. 2 B).
